summary: Whoever said the theory that TJ had no idea about the gun i agree The second the gun was announced, TJ looked shocked and...
body:
Whoever said the theory that TJ had no idea about the gun i agree

The second the gun was announced, TJ looked shocked and disturbed before Cyrus even turned around.

He would not have brought Cyrus if he knew that was going to happen. He just wanted Cyrus to go motocross with him and have a blast. However, do to peer pressure he stayed.

Note this: he did NOT pressure Cyrus to stay. He looked embarrassed and let Cyrus leave without any manipulative tactic, which was easily interpretted as really wanting cyrus to leave because he didnt want him to be there while also feeling obligated to stay. He was not disappointed in cyrus wanting to leaving, he was only disappointed in himself and circumstances

At least thats what my gut and eyes say… we’ll see
